<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗١٦٥⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2779">شُعْبَةُ، </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2540">سَلَمَةُ بْنُ كُهَيْلٍ </a>قَالَ: سَمِعْتُ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3071">الشَّعْبِيَّ </a>يُحَدِّثُ، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4500">عَلِيٍّ </a><span class="special">﵁</span>، <span class="c2">«حِينَ رَجَمَ الْمَرْأَةَ يَوْمَ الْجُمُعَةِ،<span class="c5"> وَقَالَ:</span> قَدْ رَجَمْتُهَا بِسُنَّةِ رَسُولِ اللهِ <span class="special">ﷺ</span>.»</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>